=>'Iwọn Iwọ Apoti (px)','Container Border Radius (px)'=>'Radius Iwọ Apoti (px)','Container Padding (px)'=>'Padding Apoti (px)','Inner spacing for the container'=>'Ibi inu fun apoti','Series Post Navigation'=>'Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara','Add New Series Post Navigation'=>'Fikun-un Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara tuntun','New Series Post Navigation'=>'Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara tuntun','Edit Series Post Navigation'=>'Ṣatunkọ Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara','View Series Post Navigation'=>'Wo Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara','All Series Post Navigation'=>'Gbogbo Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara','Search Series Post Navigation'=>'Wa Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara','No Series Post Navigation found.'=>'Ko si Lilọ kiri ifiweranṣẹ jara ti a ri.','No Series Post Navigation found in Trash.'=>'Ko si Iṣakoso Iwe Akọsilẹ Series ti a ri ninu Iboju idalẹnu.','Create a series to preview the navigation.'=>'Ṣẹda jara kan lati ṣe iworan iṣakoso naa.','Create posts in a series to preview the navigation.'=>'Ṣẹda awọn ifiweranṣẹ ninu jara kan lati ṣe iworan iṣakoso naa.','Sample series for preview purposes'=>'Apeere jara fun awọn idi iworan','Error updating preview.'=>'Aṣiṣe ni imudojuiwọn iworan.','Simple Navigation'=>'Iṣakoso Rọrun','Button Navigation'=>'Iṣakoso Bọtini','Image Navigation'=>'Iṣakoso Aworan','Categories'=>'Ẹka','Tags'=>'Àkíyèsí','Status'=>'Ipo','Current Part'=>'Apá Tí ń lọ','Edit'=>'Ṣatunkọ','View'=>'Wo','Trash'=>'Iboju idalẹnu','There are no published posts in this series.'=>'Ko si awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade ninu jara yii.','(Currently has no Part number)'=>'(Kosi nọmba apá lọwọlọwọ)','Preview'=>'Iworan','There are no unpublished posts in this series.'=>'Ko si awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a ko tẹjade ninu jara yii.','No Part Number'=>'Ko si Nọmba Apá','All Categories'=>'Gbogbo Ẹka','Filter'=>'Àtọka','Manage Series'=>'Ṣakoso Jara','Series'=>'Jara','Publish Series'=>'Ṣe Iwe Jara','Front View'=>'Iwo iwaju','Edit the status of %1$s'=>'Ṣatunkọ ipo ti %1$s','Series order'=>'Àtò jara','Publish or schedule posts'=>'Ṣe Iwe tabi ṣeto awọn ifiweranṣẹ','View series in frontend'=>'Wo jara ni iwaju','You have no series available.'=>'O ko ni jara ti o wa.','Add new Series.'=>'Fi Jara tuntun kun.','Create as unpublished:'=>'Ṣẹda gẹgẹbi ti a ko ṣe iwe:','When checked, all posts you assign to this series will remain unpublished until you publish the entire series.'=>'Nigbati a ba ṣe ayẹyẹ, gbogbo awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti o pin si jara yii yoo wa ni a ko ṣe iwe titi ti iwọ yoo fi ṣe iwe jara gbogbo.','The posts in your series were successfully unpublished.'=>'Awọn ifiweranṣẹ ninu jara rẹ ti a ko ṣe iwe ni aṣeyọri.','Congratulations. Your series order was updated successfully.'=>'Ẹ kú àṣeyọrí. Àtò jara rẹ ti ni imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri.','Congratulations. Your posts were published successfully.'=>'Ẹ kú àṣeyọrí. Awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ ti a ṣe iwe ni aṣeyọri.','Post moved to the Trash.'=>'Ifiweranṣẹ ti gbe lọ si Iṣan.','Congratulations. Your posts were scheduled successfully.'=>'Ẹ kú àṣeyọrí. Awọn ifiweranṣẹ rẹ ti a ṣeto ni aṣeyọri.','Manage Series Issues'=>'Ṣakoso Awọn Isoro Jara','Number of items per page'=>'Iye awọn nkan fun oju-iwe','Publishing Series:'=>'Ṣiṣẹda Jara:','Search results for &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'Awọn abajade wiwa fun &#8220;%s&#8221;','Search'=>'Wa','Publication Date/Time:'=>'Ọjọ/Àkókò Ifiṣootọ:','Update Order'=>'Ṣatunkọ Ẹlẹsẹ','Series Order:'=>'Ẹlẹsẹ Iru:','Drag the post names into the order you want them to be in the series, from the first part to the last part.'=>'Fa awọn orukọ ifiṣootọ sinu aṣẹ ti o fẹ ki wọn wa ninu ẹlẹsẹ, lati apakan akọkọ si apakan ikẹhin.','Unpublished posts in series:'=>'Awọn ifiṣootọ ti ko tii tẹjade ninu ẹlẹsẹ:','When these posts are published, they will be added after the last current post in the series.'=>'Nigbati awọn ifiṣootọ wọnyi ba tẹjade, wọn yoo wa ni afikun lẹhin ifiṣootọ lọwọlọwọ ti o kẹhin ninu ẹlẹsẹ.','Unpublished Posts'=>'Awọn Ifiṣootọ Ti Ko Ti Tẹjade','Publish Unpublished Posts'=>'Tẹjade Awọn Ifiṣootọ Ti Ko Ti Tẹjade','Unpublished Series Order'=>'Aṣẹ Ẹlẹsẹ Ti Ko Ti Tẹjade','PublishPress Series Plugin Options'=>'Àwọn aṣayan Plugin Ẹlẹsẹ PublishPress','Allowed Html'=>'Html ti a gba laaye','Overview'=>'Akopọ','The following is a legend of the tokens that are available for use in the custom template fields. These will be replaced with the appropriate values when the plugin runs.'=>'Eyi ni itumọ ti awọn ami ti o wa fun lilo ninu awọn aaye apẹrẹ aṣa. Awọn wọnyi yoo wa ni rọpo pẹlu awọn iye to yẹ nigbati plugin naa ba ṣiṣẹ.','This will be replaced with the series icon for a series.'=>'Eyi yoo wa ni rọpo pẹlu aami ẹlẹsẹ fun ẹlẹsẹ kan.','Same as %series_icon% except that the series icon will be linked to the series page'=>'Bii %series_icon% ayafi pe aami ẹlẹsẹ yoo jẹ asopọ si oju-iwe ẹlẹsẹ','This token is for use with the orgSeries widget only - it references where you want the list of series titles to be inserted and requires that the template for each series title be also set.'=>'Ami yii jẹ fun lilo pẹlu widget orgSeries nikan - o tọka si ibiti o fẹ ki atokọ awọn akọle ẹlẹsẹ ti wa ni ifọwọsi ati pe o nilo pe aṣẹ fun ọkọọkan akọle ẹlẹsẹ naa tun jẹ seti.','This will be replaced with the title of a series'=>'Eyi yoo wa ni rọpo pẹlu akọle ẹlẹsẹ kan','Same as %series_title% except that it will also be linked to the series page'=>'Bii %series_title% ayafi pe yoo tun jẹ asopọ si oju-iwe ẹlẹsẹ','Is the location token for where the contents of the post list post templates will appear.'=>'Ipo ti aami fun ibi ti akoonu ti awọn àtẹjáde akojọpọ ifiweranṣẹ yoo han.','Is the location token for where the contents of the post list post templates will appear and use provided widget post short title.'=>'Ipo ti aami fun ibi ti akoonu ti awọn àtẹjáde akojọpọ ifiweranṣẹ yoo han ati lo akọle kukuru àtẹjáde ti a pese.','Will be replaced with the post title of a post in the series'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu akọle ifiweranṣẹ ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ninu jara','Will be replaced with the post title of a post in the series linked to the page view of that post.'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu akọle ifiweranṣẹ ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ninu jara ti o ni asopọ si wiwo oju-iwe ti ifiweranṣẹ yẹn.','Will be replaced with the post title short of a post in the series'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu akọle kukuru ifiweranṣẹ ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ninu jara','Will be replaced with the post title short of a post in the series linked to the page view of that post.'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu akọle kukuru ifiweranṣẹ ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ninu jara ti o ni asopọ si wiwo oju-iwe ti ifiweranṣẹ yẹn.','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the previous post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom Previous Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu ọna asopọ lilọ fun ifiweranṣẹ ti tẹlẹ ninu jara. Ọrọ naa yoo jẹ ohun gbogbo ti a fi sinu aaye \'Ọrọ Lilọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tẹlẹ Sọtọ\'. Ti aaye yẹn ba ṣofo, lẹhinna ọrọ naa yoo jẹ akọle ifiweranṣẹ naa','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the next post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom Next Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu ọna asopọ lilọ fun ifiweranṣẹ ti n bọ ninu jara. Ọrọ naa yoo jẹ ohun gbogbo ti a fi sinu aaye \'Ọrọ Lilọ Ifiweranṣẹ Tẹlẹ Sọtọ\'. Ti aaye yẹn ba ṣofo, lẹhinna ọrọ naa yoo jẹ akọle ifiweranṣẹ naa','Will be replaced by the navigation link for the first post in a series. The text will be whatever is included in the \'Custom First Post Navigation Text\' field. If that field is empty then the text will be the title of the post'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu ọna asopọ lilọ fun ifiweranṣẹ akọkọ ninu jara. Ọrọ naa yoo jẹ ohun gbogbo ti a fi sinu aaye \'Ọrọ Lilọ Ifiweranṣẹ Kọ́kọ́ Sọtọ\'. Ti aaye yẹn ba ṣofo, lẹhinna ọrọ naa yoo jẹ akọle ifiweranṣẹ naa','Use this tag either before or after the rest of the template code.  It will indicate where you want the content of a post to display.'=>'Lo aami yii boya ṣaaju tabi lẹhin iyoku koodu àtẹjáde. Yoo tọka ibi ti o fẹ ki akoonu ifiweranṣẹ han.','Will display what part of a series the post is'=>'Yoo fihan iru apakan jara ti ifiweranṣẹ jẹ','Will display the total number of posts in a series'=>'Yoo fihan nọmba lapapọ ti awọn ifiweranṣẹ ninu jara','Will display the description for the series'=>'Yoo fihan apejuwe fun jara','Will output the slug of the series'=>'Yoo funni ni slug ti jara','Will output the ID of the series'=>'Yoo funni ni ID ti jara','Will output the author of the post'=>'Yoo funni ni onkọwe ifiweranṣẹ naa','If the post has a feature-image then that image will be displayed'=>'Ti ifiweranṣẹ ba ni aworan ẹya, lẹhinna aworan yẹn yoo han','The date that a post was published'=>'Ọjọ ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ti wa ni atẹjade','Will be replaced with the unpublished post title of a post in the series'=>'A yoo rọpo rẹ pẹlu akọle ifiweranṣẹ ti ko tẹjade ti ifiweranṣẹ kan ninu jara','Will display the total number of published and unpublished posts in a series'=>'Yoo fihan nọmba lapapọ ti awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti a tẹjade ati ti ko tẹjade ninu jara','Update Options'=>'Awọn aṣayan imudojuiwọn','Clicking Yes will reset the options to the defaults and you will lose all customizations. Or you can click cancel and return.'=>'Tite Yes yoo tun awọn aṣayan pada si awọn aiyipada ati pe iwọ yoo padanu gbogbo awọn aṣa. Tabi o le tẹ ipinnu ati pada.','No'=>'Bẹẹkọ','Yes'=>'Bẹẹni','Please update your PublishPress Series data'=>'Jọwọ mu data PublishPress Series rẹ pọ si','We have made changes to how series are stored and this requires a small update. This improves support for the Multiple Series feature, and resolves some issues with the order of posts. Please click this button to upgrade.'=>'A ti ṣe awọn ayipada si bi awọn jara ti wa ni fipamọ ati eyi nilo imudojuiwọn kekere kan. Eyi mu atilẹyin fun ẹya Multiple Series pọ si, ati pe o yanju diẹ ninu awọn iṣoro pẹlu ìtòsọna awọn ifiweranṣẹ. Jọwọ tẹ bọtini yii lati ṣe imudojuiwọn.','Update Series data'=>'Mudarasi data Series','Series upgrade completed.'=>'Imudojuiwọn jara ti pari.','Series order sync completed. %d posts updated.'=>'Iṣọpọ ìtòsọna jara ti pari. %d awọn ifiweranṣẹ ti ni imudojuiwọn.','taxonomy general nameSeries'=>'Jara','taxonomy singular nameSeries'=>'Jara','Search Series'=>'Wa Jara','Popular Series'=>'Awọn Jara Olokiki','All Series'=>'Gbogbo Awọn Jara','Edit Series'=>'Ṣatunkọ Jara','Update Series'=>'Mudarasi Jara','Add New Series'=>'Fi Jara Tuntun Kun','New Series Name'=>'Orukọ Jara Tuntun','No series found'=>'Ko si jara ti a rii','%1$s series migrated from "%2$s" to "%3$s" taxonomy. Settings updated.'=>'%1$s jara ti yipada lati "%2$s" si "%3$s" taxonomy. Awọn eto ti ni imudojuiwọn.','PublishPress Series Plugin Options have been updated'=>'Awọn aṣayan Plugin PublishPress Series ti ni imudojuiwọn','Permission denied'=>'Iwe-aṣẹ kọ','PublishPress Series Plugin Options have been RESET'=>'Aṣayan Plugin PublishPress Series ti wa ni TUNṣe','Please change these settings carefully as they make significant changes to PublishPress Series.'=>'Jọwọ yipada awọn eto wọnyi pẹlu iṣọra bi wọn ṣe ṣe awọn ayipada pataki si PublishPress Series.','Series Settings'=>'Awọn Eto Series','Delete all PublishPress Series data from the database when deleting this plugin.'=>'Pa gbogbo data PublishPress Series kuro ninu ibi ipamọ nigba ti o ba n pa plugin yii.','Series Upgrade'=>'Imudojuiwọn Series','Run Upgrade Task'=>'Ṣiṣejade Iṣẹ Imudojuiwọn','In version 2.11.4, PublishPress Series made changes to how series are stored. You can run the upgrade task here if you\'re having issues with series parts.'=>'Ninu ẹya 2.11.4, PublishPress Series ṣe awọn ayipada si bi a ṣe n pa awọn series. O le ṣiṣẹ iṣẹ imudojuiwọn nibi ti o ba ni awọn iṣoro pẹlu awọn ẹya series.','Sync Series Order to Menu Order'=>'Sopọ Ibere Series si Ibere Menu','Sync to Menu Order'=>'Sopọ si Ibere Menu','This will sync all series part numbers to WordPress menu_order field. Useful for themes/page builders that can only sort by menu order (Page Attributes: Order). This allows you to use native WordPress ordering instead of custom fields.'=>'Eyi yoo sopọ gbogbo awọn nọmba ẹya series si aaye menu_order ti WordPress. Wulo fun awọn akori/olugbasilẹ oju-iwe ti o le ṣe irọrun nikan nipasẹ ibere menu (Awọn Attribut Oju: Ibere). Eyi gba ọ laaye lati lo ibere WordPress abinibi dipo awọn aaye aṣa.','Reset settings'=>'Tun awọn eto','Reset options to default'=>'Tun awọn aṣayan si aiyipada','Legacy'=>'Itan','Legacy Settings'=>'Awọn Eto Itan','Default'=>'Aiyipada','CSS Styles'=>'Awọn Ara CSS','Use PublishPress Series CSS styles?'=>'Lo awọn ara CSS PublishPress Series?','Style options'=>'Awọn aṣayan ara','Use default style'=>'Lo ara aiyipada','Use box style'=>'Lo ara apoti','Use dark style'=>'Lo aṣa dudu','Use light style'=>'Lo aṣa imọlẹ','Series Overview'=>'Akopọ Ẹ̀ka','Choose the design for the taxonomy page where a single Series is displayed.'=>'Yan apẹrẹ fun oju-iwe taxonomy ti a fi ẹ̀ka kan han.','Layout:'=>'Ilana:','Choosing a layout different to "Default" will override the taxonomy template from your theme. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here for details on how to customize these designs</a>.'=>'Yiyan ilana ti o yatọ si "Ibi isalẹ" yoo kọja awoṣe taxonomy lati inu akori rẹ. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Tẹ nibi fun alaye lori bi a ṣe le ṣe atunṣe awọn apẹrẹ wọnyi</a>.','Columns:'=>'Awọn ọwọn:','Order series by:'=>'Paṣẹ ẹ̀ka nipasẹ:','Series part'=>'Apá ẹ̀ka','Order by date'=>'Paṣẹ nipasẹ ọjọ','Series order method'=>'Ọna paṣẹ ẹ̀ka','Series Table of Contents'=>'Atokọ Akọkọ Ẹ̀ka','Series Table of Contents URL:'=>'URL Atokọ Akọkọ Ẹ̀ka:','view page'=>'wo oju-iwe','You must %1s update your permalink structure %2s to something other than "Plain" for the Series Table of Contents URL to work.'=>'O gbọdọ %1s ṣe imudojuiwọn ilana permalink rẹ %2s si nkan miiran ju "Pẹ̀lú" lọ ki URL Atokọ Akọkọ Ẹ̀ka le ṣiṣẹ.','Series Per Page:'=>'Ẹ̀ka Fun Oju-iwe:','Series Table of Contents Title:'=>'Ak标题 Atokọ Akọkọ Ẹ̀ka:','Series Icons'=>'Àwòrán Ẹ̀ka','Width for icon on series table of contents page (in pixels)'=>'Iwọn fun àwòrán lori oju-iwe atokọ ẹ̀ka (ninu awọn piksẹli)','Width for icon on a post page (in pixels).'=>'Iwọn fun àwòrán lori oju-iwe ifiweranṣẹ (ninu awọn piksẹli).','Width for icon if displayed via the latest series template (in pixels).'=>'Iwọn fun aami ti a ba ṣe afihan nipasẹ awoṣe jara tuntun (ni pixels).','Latest Series'=>'Jara Tuntun','This display is used by the "Latest Series" widget.'=>'Iṣafihan yii ni a lo nipasẹ "Jara Tuntun" widget.','Latest Series (tags before):'=>'Jara Tuntun (awọn aami ṣaaju):','Latest Series (inner tags):'=>'Jara Tuntun (awọn aami inu):','Latest Series (tags after):'=>'Jara Tuntun (awọn aami lẹhin):','This display is used by the "Series Table of Contents" widget, shortcode, and URL.'=>'Iṣafihan yii ni a lo nipasẹ "Tabili Akopọ Jara" widget, shortcode, ati URL.','This display is used by the "Series Table of Contents". To find the URL for this display, go the "Display" tab and then "Series Table of Contents URL".'=>'Iṣafihan yii ni a lo nipasẹ "Tabili Akopọ Jara". Lati wa URL fun iṣafihan yii, lọ si taabu "Iṣafihan" ki o si "Tabili Akopọ Jara URL".','These settings allow you to customize the metabox on the post editing screen.'=>'Awọn eto wọnyi gba ọ laaye lati ṣe akanṣe metabox lori iboju ṣiṣatunkọ ifiweranṣẹ.','Default Series Order'=>'Aṣẹ Jara Aiyipada','Alphabetical A-Z'=>'A-Z nipasẹ Alifabeeti','Alphabetical Z-A'=>'Z-A nipasẹ Alifabeeti','Show "Add New"'=>'Fihan "Fikun-un Tuntun"','Show "Post title in widget"'=>'Fihan "Orukọ ifiweranṣẹ ninu widget"','Metabox Series Order'=>'Aṣẹ Metabox Jara','Post Details Settings'=>'Eto Awọn alaye Ifiweranṣẹ','Configure the Series Post Details display shown on posts in a series.'=>'Ṣeto iṣafihan Awọn alaye Ifiweranṣẹ Jara ti a fihan lori awọn ifiweranṣẹ ninu jara kan.','As in Template'=>'Gẹgẹbi ninu Awoṣe','Display Series Post Details?'=>'Ṣiṣafihan Awọn alaye Ifiweranṣẹ Jara?','Post Details Selection'=>'Yiyan Awọn alaye Ifiweranṣẹ','Edit this layout'=>'Ṣatunkọ àtẹ̀jáde yìí','Loading…'=>'Nṣiṣẹ…','Post Details Position'=>'Ipò Àlàyé Fífi','Series Meta Template'=>'Àtẹ̀jáde Meta Ẹ̀kó','Series Meta (with excerpts)'=>'Meta Ẹ̀kó (pẹlu àpẹẹrẹ)','Limit to single page only'=>'Dín kún ẹ̀ka kan ṣoṣo','Whether to limit series meta display to single page only or include archive page.'=>'Báwo ni a ṣe fẹ́ dín àfihàn meta ẹ̀kó kún ẹ̀ka kan ṣoṣo tàbí kó àtẹ̀jáde ìkànsí kún.','Post List Box Settings'=>'Àwọn Àtọ́kà Post List Box','Configure the Post List Box that displays all posts in a series.'=>'Ṣe àtúnṣe àtọ́kà Post List Box tí ń fi gbogbo àwọn àkọsílẹ̀ hàn nínú ẹ̀kó kan.','Display Post List Boxes?'=>'Ṣe àfihàn Àtọ́kà Post List Boxes?','Post List Boxes Selection'=>'Yiyan Àtọ́kà Post List Boxes','Edit this box'=>'Ṣatunkọ àpoti yìí','Post List Box Position'=>'Ipò Àtọ́kà Post List Box','Series Post List Template'=>'Àtẹ̀jáde Àtẹ́wọ́ Post List Ẹ̀kó','Post Title (Linked Post)'=>'Àkọlé Post (Post Tí a So)','Post Title (Current Post)'=>'Àkọlé Post (Post Tí o Wà Lọwọ́lọwọ)','Navigation'=>'Iṣàkóso','Navigation Settings'=>'Àtọ́kà Iṣàkóso','Configure the Series Navigation display shown on posts in a series.'=>'Ṣe àtúnṣe àfihàn Iṣàkóso Ẹ̀kó tí a fi hàn lórí àwọn àkọsílẹ̀ nínú ẹ̀kó kan.','Display Series Navigation?'=>'Ṣe àfihàn Iṣàkóso Ẹ̀kó?','Navigation Selection'=>'Yiyan Irin-ajo','Navigation Position'=>'Ipo Irin-ajo','Navigation Template'=>'Awoṣe Irin-ajo','Next Post Text'=>'Ọrọ Iposti Tó Ń Bọ','Previous Post Text'=>'Ọrọ Iposti Tó Ṣáájú','First Post Text'=>'Ọrọ Iposti Àkọ́kọ́','Post Types'=>'Iru Ifiweranṣẹ','Custom Post Type Support'=>'Support Irú Akọsilẹ̀ Àdáni','Enable PublishPress Series for custom post types.'=>'Mú Ẹ̀rọ PublishPress Series ṣiṣẹ́ fún irú akọsilẹ̀ àdáni.','Pro Features'=>'Àwọn ẹya Pro','These settings allow you enable or disable features in PublishPress Series Pro.'=>'Àwọn eto wọ̀nyí jẹ́ kí o ní ànfààní tàbí kó pa àwọn ẹya mọ́ nínú PublishPress Series Pro.','Allow custom post types to be used with PublishPress Series.'=>'Gba irú akọsilẹ̀ àdáni láti lo pẹ̀lú PublishPress Series.','Shortcodes'=>'Koodu Kékèké','Provides shortcodes to display series information.'=>'N pese koodu kékèké láti fi hàn ìmọ̀ràn series.','Extra Tokens'=>'Àwọn Ọ̀rọ̀ Tó Kù','Provides extra tokens to customize the output of series information.'=>'N pese àwọn ọrọ̀ tó kù láti ṣe àtúnṣe àbájáde ìmọ̀ràn series.','Multiple Series'=>'Ọpọ̀ Series','Allows authors to add posts to more than one series.'=>'Gba àwọn onkọ̀wé láti fi àwọn ìposti kún diẹ ẹ̀dá ẹgbẹ̀run kan.','Series Category'=>'Ẹ̀ka Series','Settings for Series Categories archive URL and display behavior.'=>'Àwọn eto fún URL ìkànsí Ẹ̀ka Series àti ihuwasi àfihàn.','Series Categories URL Base:'=>'Ibi URL Ẹ̀ka Series:','This text will be used in Series Categories archive URLs. If you change it, old URLs will be redirected to the new base.'=>'Ọrọ yìí máa ṣee lo nínú URL ìkànsí Ẹ̀ka Series. Tí o bá yí i padà, awọn URL atijọ́ máa ṣe àtúnṣe sí ibi tuntun.','Series Categories Archive Template:'=>'Awoṣe Ibi ipamọ Ẹka jara:','Use template from Theme'=>'Lo awoṣe lati Theme','Use template from Plugin'=>'Lo awoṣe lati Plugin','Theme template uses your active theme template hierarchy. Plugin template uses PublishPress Series fallback design when your theme does not provide taxonomy-series_group.php.'=>'Awoṣe theme nlo ilana awoṣe theme ti o wa lọwọlọwọ. Awoṣe plugin nlo apẹrẹ isalẹ PublishPress Series nigbati theme rẹ ko pese taxonomy-series_group.php.','Plugin Template Display Options:'=>'Awọn aṣayan Ifihan Awoṣe Plugin:','Show Series Icon'=>'Fihan Aami Jara','Show Series Description'=>'Fihan Apejuwe Jara','Show Posts in each Series as list items'=>'Fihan Awọn ifiweranṣẹ ni gbogbo Jara gẹgẹ bi awọn nkan akojọ','This feature allows you to create a new taxonomy for this plugin to use if you don\'t want to use the default "Series" taxonomy.'=>'Iwa yii n jẹ ki o ṣẹda taxonomy tuntun fun plugin yii lati lo ti o ko ba fẹ lo taxonomy "Jara" aiyipada.','Series Taxonomy Slug:'=>'Slug Taxonomy Jara:','This text will be part of the series base URL.'=>'Ọrọ yii yoo jẹ apakan ti URL ipilẹ jara.','Series Taxonomy:'=>'Taxonomy Jara:','To create a new taxonomy, enter the new name and click the "Update Options" button.'=>'Lati ṣẹda taxonomy tuntun, tẹ orukọ tuntun ki o si tẹ bọtini "Imudojuiwọn Awọn aṣayan".','Migrate Terms'=>'Gbe Awọn ọrọ','Automatically migrate existing series terms to the new taxonomy'=>'Gbe awọn ọrọ jara to wa tẹlẹ laifọwọyi si taxonomy tuntun','If checked, all terms from the current taxonomy will be migrated to the new taxonomy when you change the taxonomy slug. If unchecked, only the taxonomy slug will be changed.'=>'Ti o ba ti ṣayẹwo, gbogbo awọn ọrọ lati taxonomy ti o wa lọwọlọwọ yoo gbe si taxonomy tuntun nigbati o ba yi slug taxonomy pada. Ti o ko ba ṣayẹwo, slug taxonomy nikan ni yoo yipada.','Sorry, no results found.'=>'E ma binu, ko si awọn esi ti a ri.','You\'re using PublishPress Series Free. The Pro version has more features and support. %sUpgrade to Pro%s'=>'O nlo PublishPress Series Free. Ẹya Pro ni awọn ẹya diẹ sii ati atilẹyin. %sGbadun si Pro%s','Upgrade to Pro'=>'Gbadun si Pro','Need PublishPress Series Support?'=>'Nilo Atilẹyin PublishPress Series?','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'Ti o ba nilo iranlọwọ tabi ni ibeere ẹya tuntun, jọwọ jẹ ki a mọ.','Request Support'=>'Beere Atilẹyin','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ alaye tun wa lori oju opo wẹẹbu amugbooro naa.','View Knowledge Base'=>'Wo Ipilẹ Ọgbọ́n','An error occured'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ṣẹlẹ','%1$s series migrated to new taxonomy'=>'%1$s jara ti a gbe lọ si imọ-ẹrọ tuntun','If you like %s, please leave us a %s rating. Thank you!'=>'Ti o ba fẹ %s, jọwọ fi %s ìwọn kan silẹ fun wa. O ṣeun!','About PublishPress Series'=>'Nipa PublishPress Jara','About'=>'Nipa','PublishPress Series Documentation'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ PublishPress Jara','Documentation'=>'Iwe afọwọkọ','Contact the PublishPress team'=>'Kan si ẹgbẹ PublishPress','Contact'=>'Kan si','Sorry but you don\'t have permission to add series'=>'E ma binu ṣugbọn o ko ni igbanilaaye lati fi jara kun','The name you picked isn\'t sanitizing correctly. Try something different.'=>'Orukọ ti o yan ko ni imukuro ni deede. Gbiyanju nkan miiran.','Hmm... it looks like there is already a series with that name. Try something else'=>'Hmm... o dabi pe jara kan ti wa pẹlu orukọ yẹn. Gbiyanju nkan miiran','Not part of a series'=>'Kii ṣe apakan jara','Search series'=>'Wa jara','Series Part:'=>'Apakan Jara:','Post title in widget:'=>'Akole ifiweranṣẹ ninu widget:','A short title of this post that will be used in the Series widget. Leave blank to use the full title.'=>'Akọle kukuru ti ifiweranṣẹ yii ti a yoo lo ninu widget Series. Fi silẹ silẹ lati lo akọle pipe.','series meta box titleSeries'=>'Jara','posts list column headerSeries'=>'Jara','<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a> (No part number)'=>'<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a> (Ko si nọmba apakan)','<a href="%3$s" title="%4$s">%5$s</a> (Part %1$s of %2$s)'=>'<a href="%3$s" title="%4$s">%5$s</a> (Apakan %1$s ti %2$s)','<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a>  (No Part Number)'=>'<a href="%1$s" title="%2$s">%3$s</a>  (Ko si Nọmba Apakan)','No Series'=>'Ko si Series','View all series'=>'Wo gbogbo awọn jara','Manage All Series'=>'Ṣakoso Gbogbo Awọn Jara','dashboard count labelSeries'=>'Jara','Term Order'=>'Ilana Ọrọ','To reposition an item, drag and drop the row by "clicking and holding" it anywhere and moving it to its new position.'=>'Lati tun ipo nkan kan, fa ati tu ila pẹlu "titẹ ati mimu" rẹ ni ibikibi ki o si gbe e si ipo titun rẹ.','ID'=>'ID','Terms are usually ordered alphabetically, but you can choose your own order by entering a number (1 for first, etc.) in this field.'=>'Awọn ọrọ nigbagbogbo ni a paṣẹ ni lẹta, ṣugbọn o le yan ilana tirẹ nipa titẹ nọmba kan (1 fun akọkọ, bbl) ni aaye yii.','Current series icon:'=>'Aami jara lọwọlọwọ:','No icon currently'=>'Ko si aami lọwọlọwọ','Delete image? (note: there will not be an image associated with this series if you select this)'=>'Pa aworan? (akọsilẹ: ko si aworan ti o ni nkan ṣe pẹlu jara yii ti o ba yan eyi)','Series Icon Upload:'=>'Gbe aami Jara:','Upload an image for the series.'=>'Gbe aworan kan fun jara naa.','Invalid form data'=>'Data fọọmu ti ko tọ','Invalid nonce, reload and try again'=>'Nonce ti ko tọ, tun gbe e ki o si gbiyanju lẹẹkansi','Invalid taxonomy'=>'Taxonomy ti ko tọ','Not enough permission'=>'Iwe-aṣẹ ti ko to','Updated successfully'=>'Ti a ṣe imudojuiwọn ni aṣeyọri','Settings'=>'Àwọn àṣàyàn','PublishPress Series Options'=>'Àwọn aṣayan PublishPress Series','top-level admin menu labelSeries'=>'Jara','Taxonomy'=>'Taxonomy','Metabox'=>'Metabox','Advanced'=>'Ijinle','Select "Not part of a series" to remove any series data from post'=>'Yan "Kò jẹ́ apá ti jara" lati yọ eyikeyi data jara kuro ninu ifiweranṣẹ','taxonomy menu nameSeries'=>'Jara','&larr; Go to Series'=>'&larr; Lọ si Jara','View Series'=>'Wo Jara','Series List'=>'Atokọ Jara','Series Link'=>'Lọ́ńkò Jara','A link to a Series'=>'Akọ́kọ́ sí Jara kan','leave the %tokens% as is when translatingThis entry is part %series_part% of %total_posts_in_series% in the series '=>'Iwọnyi jẹ apakan %series_part% ti %total_posts_in_series% ninu jara ','Series Navigation'=>'Iṣàkóso Jara','Series: '=>'Jara: ','Posts from the series: '=>'Àwọn ifiweranṣẹ lati jara: ','series list titleSeries'=>'Jara','Series:'=>'Jara:','Part:'=>'Apá:','All the Series I\'ve Written'=>'Gbogbo Jara tí mo ti kọ','<a href="%s" title="%s">Series</a>'=>'<a href="%s" title="%s">Jara</a>','Auto/None'=>'Auto/Ko si','Use this to control the output of the latest series widget'=>'Lo eyi lati ṣakoso iṣẹjade ti widget jara tuntun julọ','Most Recent Series'=>'Jara Tuntun Jùlọ','Title:'=>'Ak title:','The layout and content of this widget can be adjusted via the <a href="%s">Latest Serie