g>Àwọn àfikún yìí lè parẹ.</strong>','The %1$s already has a parameter indexed with the name: %2$s.'=>'%1$s ti ni paramita kan tó ti n ṣàkóso pẹ̀lú orúkọ: %2$s.','The %1$s method can only be used to register a child of %2$s.'=>'Ọna %1$s lè jẹ́ kí a lo láti forúkọsílẹ ọmọ %2$s kan nìkan.','Unable to retrieve an instance of %1$s. Not found.'=>'Kò le gba àpẹẹrẹ %1$s. Kò rí.','%1$s is not a valid entity (expected: %2$s).'=>'%1$s kì í ṣe ẹ̀dá tó wúlò (tí a nírètí: %2$s).','The "%1$s" file is either missing or could not be read due to permissions. Please ensure that the following path is correct and verify that the file permissions are correct:%2$s %3$s'=>'Fáìlì "%1$s" tàbí kò sí tàbí kò lè ka nitori awọn àṣẹ. Jọwọ jẹ́ kó dájú pé ọ̀nà yìí tọ́ àti ṣàdédé pé àwọn àṣẹ fáìlì náà tọ́:%2$s %3$s','%s does not exist or is not reachable.'=>'%s kò sí tàbí kò lè dé.','Nonce fail.'=>'Aṣiṣe nonce.','The provided object fully qualified class name (%1$s) must implement the %2$s interface.'=>'Orúkọ kilasi tí a fúnni (%1$s) gbọ́dọ̀ ṣe àfihàn %2$s interface.','The given file path (%s) is not readable.'=>'Ọ̀nà fáìlì tí a fúnni (%s) kò lè ka.','An error occurred, please try again.'=>'Aṣiṣe kan ṣẹlẹ̀, jọwọ tún gbìmọ̀.','The incoming value for %1$s is expected to be a closure.  It was not.'=>'Iye tí ń bọ fún %1$s ni a nírètí láti jẹ́ àkópọ. Kò jẹ́ bẹ́ẹ̀.','Deactivate License'=>'Dákẹ́kọ́ Àṣẹ','Activate License'=>'Ṣíṣe Àṣẹ','License Key successfully activated.'=>'Bọtini Àṣẹ ti ṣe àfikún pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí.','License Key successfully deactivated.'=>'Bọtini Àṣẹ ti dákẹ́kọ́ pẹ̀lú aṣeyọrí.','The value for %1$s is already set and it is not an array. The %2$s method can only be used to push values to this data element when it is an array.'=>'Iye fún %1$s ti ṣàtúnṣe tẹlẹ̀ àti kò jẹ́ àkópọ. Ọna %2$s lè jẹ́ kí a lo láti fi iye kun àkópọ yìí nígbà tí ó bá jẹ́ àkópọ.','The value for %1$s already exists in the %2$s property. Overrides are not allowed. Since the value of this data is an array, you may want to use the %3$s method to push your value to the array.'=>'Iye fún %1$s ti wà ní %2$s ohun-ini. Àtúnṣeto kì í ṣe àfihàn. Níwọ̀n bí iye data yìí ṣe jẹ́ àkópọ, o lè fẹ́ lo ọ̀nà %3$s láti fi iye rẹ sí àkópọ náà.','The value for %1$s already exists in the %2$s property. Overrides are not allowed.  Consider attaching your value to a different key'=>'Iye fun %1$s ti wa ni tẹlẹ ninu ohun-ini %2$s. Awọn ikolu ko gba laaye. Ronu nipa fifi iye rẹ si bọtini miiran','The namespace for this manifest file has already been registered, choose a namespace other than %s'=>'A ti forukọsilẹ orukọ aaye fun faili manifest yi, yan orukọ aaye miiran ju %s lọ','The provided value for %1$s is not a valid url.  The url provided was: %2$s'=>'Iye ti a pese fun %1$s kii ṣe url to wulo. Url ti a pese ni: %2$s','License Key for %1$s'=>'Bọtini Iwe-aṣẹ fun %1$s','Enter your license key: '=>'Tẹ bọtini iwe-aṣẹ rẹ: ']];